Package: MediadoR
Type: Package
Title: A tool to research Brazilian collective bargaining
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gabriel Pistelli Ferreira
Maintainer: Gabriel Pistelli Ferreira <gabriel.pistelli.ferreira@gmail.com>
Description: A proto-package (still in development) to organize researches on MTE's Mediador platform, focusing in trends and conditions of collective bargaining. Offers functions to scrape and wrangle data from collective bargaining documents.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: rvest, stringr, magrittr
Suggests: dplyr, ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
